au.gov.amsa.geo.distance

Class OperatorEffectiveSpeedFilter

  • java.lang.Object
    • au.gov.amsa.geo.distance.OperatorEffectiveSpeedFilter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    rx.functions.Func1<rx.Subscriber<? super Fix>,rx.Subscriber<? super Fix>>, rx.functions.Function, rx.Observable.Operator<Fix,Fix>

    public class OperatorEffectiveSpeedFilter
extends Object
implements rx.Observable.Operator<Fix,Fix>
    Given a sequence of fixes the first fix is consider to be the first fix that passes an effective speed check with its following fix. Having established the first fix then following fixes are discarded from the sequence that fail the effective speed check with the last confirmed fix.
